How to use:
1. Download everything
2. Open quote-img-maker.htm in browser
3. Click the white box on the left
4. Type or paste something
5. Adjust overall font size on the right
6. Or do details adjustment with the rich text toolbar
7. When you finish, click 'Save file'
8. Right click > Save
9. Click anywhere to go back to editor

Tested in Google Chrome 26.0.1410.64 m (26/4/2013). Still have many bugs.